" MESSAGE 01.22.108 "

Usually the transmitter made only noise, sometimes the radio turned on. It seems like a useless thing, I thought to throw it away, but at that moment something spoke and was imprinted here. It's not for me to take responsibility and say what it was. Everything can be...
